			        <br>&nbsp; Master Dome Stadium - 
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Circle, L1, L1, R1, R2, L2, X, Square, Square, R1, R2, R1, R2, Triangle, L2, R1, L2, Circle, L2, R2, R1, X, L1, R2, Square, L2, R1, X, R1, R1</font>&nbsp;
			        <br>&nbsp; Last Game of the Tournament - 
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">X, Square, Square, R1, R2, R1, R2, Triangle, L2, R1, L2, Circle, L2, R2, R1, X, L1, R2, Square, L2, R1, X, R1, R1, Circle, L1, L1, R1, R2, L2</font>&nbsp;
			        <br>&nbsp; Shrinking Rotofoil - 
